maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: The rough gem in the west. Home to collectors and the Shad.
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: La Gemme Rugueuse de l'ouest. Maison des collectionneurs et des Shads.

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: - \c[3]Ba'kii Kum\c[0] -
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: - \c[3]\v[area.heat-village.name]\c[0] -

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Dourk
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Dourk

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Dourk
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Dourk

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Anything wrong?\. I'm just sitting here.
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Qu'est-ce qu'il y a ?\. Je suis juste assis ici.

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Hi!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Salut !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: C-crimes in the bazaar?\. What are you talking about?\. I don't know anything!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Des crimes dans le bazar ?\. De quoi vous parlez ?\. Je sais rien de tout ça !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: So it was you on the communicator?\. Damn that Billston...
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Donc c'était toi sur le communicateur ?\. Ce satané Billston...

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: I thought someone as ruthless as him would at least be more careful.
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: J'aurais pensé qu'un type impitoyable comme lui ferait un peu plus attention à ses affaires.

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: He roped me into this, I swear!\. Told me about all the money, threatened me if I refused, all that!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Il m'a entrainé là-dedans, je vous le jure !\. Il m'a parlé de tout l'argent qu'il y a à se faire et m'a menacé si jamais je refusais et tout !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: "No one will care about it,"\. he said. "Those scaly idiots don't know how to handle the money anyway!"\. So much for that.
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: "Personne ne s'y intéressera."\. Qu'il disait. "Ces idiots d'écailles ne savent pas gérer leur argent de toute façon !"\. Tout ça pour ça.

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Well, time to come clean then, I suppose.\. At least I can bring down that jerk with me.
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Bon, il est temps de faire mes bagages et de me racheter, j'imagine.\. Au moins je peux faire tomber ce salopard avec moi !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Dourk
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Dourk

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Billston
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Billston

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Well, well, well.\. Where might you lot be going?
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Bien, bien, bien.\. Où est-ce que vous comptiez aller comme ça ?

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Hi!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Salut !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: I knew something was wrong once I noticed my communicator missing.\. You \v[lore.title.seeker]s are a sneaky lot, hm?
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Je savais qu'il se tramait quelque chose dès l'instant où j'ai perdu mon communicateur.\. Vous les \v[lore.title.seeker]s vous êtes plutôt du genre discret, hein ?

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Forget it, man!\. You messed up!\. This is over!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Oublie ça, mec !\. T'as merdé !\. C'est terminé !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: It is,\.\. r-\.right...?
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: C'est terminé,\.\. h-hein... ?

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Oh, for you it is.\. Me, though?\.\. I prepared something special just for moments like this!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Oh, ça l'est pour toi, oui.\. Mais pour moi ?\.\. J'ai déjà préparé quelque chose de spécial pour parer à une telle éventualité !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Dourk
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Dourk

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Billston
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Billston

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: This will be the end of you and no one will ever know the truth!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Ce sera la fin pour vous et jamais personne ne connaitra la vérité !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: D-dude, look where we are...\.\. this is madness!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: M-mec, regarde où on est...\.\. C'est de la folie !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Silence!\. These expensive preparations won't go to waste.\.\. And I'm out of here!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Silence !\. Ces préparations couteuses n'auront pas été en vain.\.\. Moi je me tire d'ici !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Bye!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Bye !

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Dourk
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Dourk

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: W-well... you know how to handle this, right?
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: B-Bon... Tu sais déjà quoi faire, hein ?

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.orig: Good... so... I'll just be hiding around that corner.\. Good luck!
maps/arena/faction/baki-bots-1.json/enti.text: Bien... Donc euh... moi je vais me cacher derrière ce coin.\. Bonne chance !

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: Come back here to get your reward!
Greetings, \v[lore.title.seeker]. I have to keep watch on the harbor and protect our citizens, so please excuse me.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Bonjour, \v[lore.title.seeker]. Il faut que je monte la garde au port pour protéger nos citoyens, donc, si vous pouviez m'excuser.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: Hello, \v[lore.title.seeker].\. I assume they sent you to help me investigate this smuggling case?
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Bonjour \v[lore.title.seeker].\. J'imagine qu'on vous a envoyé en renfort pour m'aider à enquêter sur les trafics ?

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: Excellent.\. I want you to examine the crates on the eastern part of the harbor.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Excellent.\. J'aimerais que vous vérifiiez les caisses de la partie est du port.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: The data signature of the suspicious goods has already been sent to you, so you should be able to sense it.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Les données de signature des marchandises suspectes vous ont déjà été transmises, donc vous devriez pouvoir les localiser.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: I'll be here investigating our leads to potential culprits.\. Come back when you've found something.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Je vais rester ici et explorer d'autres pistes.\. Revenez ici si vous trouvez quelque chose.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: The crate should be somewhere around here so you better find it!
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: La caisse devrait se trouver quelque part dans les parages, vous feriez mieux de le trouver !

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: You go find that suspicious dockworker!\. I'll make sure he doesn't leave for the city.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Il faut que vous trouviez ce docker louche !\. Je vais m'assurer qu'il ne quitte pas le port.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: Well met, \v[lore.title.seeker]. There has been no further trouble at the docks so far but we should stay vigilant.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Bien joué, \v[lore.title.seeker]rr. Il n'y a pas eu d'autres problèmes pour l'instant, mais il faut rrrester vigilant.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: Sacrebleu! Why would they add a door there?!
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Sacrebleu ! Pourquoi est-ce qu'il fallait qu'ils mettent une porte ici ?

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: This door honestly just went where it was supposed to. Very consistent.
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: Cette porte mène vraiment là ou il fallait qu'elle mène. C'est cohérent.

maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.orig: What was that? Did they honestly design it that way?
maps/arena/faction/rh-turrets-1.json/ent.text: C'était quoi ça ? Ils l'ont vraiment conçu comme ça ?
